    <category>
        <pattern>_</pattern>
        <that>If you were starting the day off like our hero, how would you be feeling?</that>
        <template>
            Yes, <get name = "hero"/> feels <star/>.
            Most of all, <get name = "hero"/> is perplexed, especially after arriving at the office only to find on the
            sign on the locked entrance door which reads OFFICE SPACE AVAILABLE.
            <get name = "hero"/> is shocked, wondering if twenty years have truly passed by.
            <get name = "hero"/> returns home, head spinning.
            Thinking back, <get name = "hero"/> suddenly remembers the big project that a friend, Robert, had been working on.
            The project had to do with time, but the details are fuzzy, <get name = "hero"/> cannot quite remember.
            Does <get name = "hero"/> decide to contact Robert, or does <get name = "hero"/> go back to bed.
            hoping that all of this is a weird dream?
            <oob><robot></robot></oob>
        </template>
    </category>

